task.summary: Create classes to store a data set.
Location should be in geography package.
Create an importer for twitter json files.
Set up fields of the model and the node.
Implement the bivariate normal distribution and the univariate one.
Add the dictionary to Model and allow importers to read and extend based on existing dictionary.
